      "committedDate": "2026-05-25T22:39:20Z",
      "messageBody": "Inject MastraCode runtime state into Harness v1 shared workspace initialization so workspace factories can resolve the project path during startup.\n\nMatch the legacy Harness internal Mastra logger behavior to avoid surfacing expected observability storage capability warnings in the TUI, and only attach the local storage exporter when local tracing storage is active.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Mastra Code (openai/gpt-5.5) <noreply@mastra.ai>",
