      "committedDate": "2026-05-25T23:53:58Z",
      "messageBody": "Register request_access prompts through the native Harness v1 sandbox-access path and preserve those pending resumes instead of downgrading them to generic tool suspensions.\n\nRebuild resume request context with model, memory, toolsets, and approval state so approved sandbox requests continue the original run. Propagate the MastraCode workspace factory onto v1 agents so resumed and follow-up turns keep local workspace tools available.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Mastra Code (openai/gpt-5.5) <noreply@mastra.ai>",
